<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.9.8">
<l>poruntala ṉākam puḷḷuvan tēṟa vaḷḷuki rālpiḷan taṉṟu</l>
<l>peruntakaik kiraṅki vāliyai muṉinta perumaiko lōceyta tiṉṟu</l>
<l>peruntaṭaṅ kaṇṇi curumpuṟu kōtai perumaiyai niṉaintilai pēcil</l>
<l>karuṅkaṭal vaṇṇā kavuḷkoṇṭa nīrā mivaḷeṉak karutukiṉ ṟāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What you did here, is it [with] the nobility that raged against Vāli,</l>
<l rend="indent">pitying great, worthy [Sugrīva,]</l>
<l>Having once split with your sharp claws the chest of your opponent,</l>
<l rend="indent">so that vultures gladly climbed [on it]?</l>
<l>You do not consider the nobility of her with large eyes</l>
<l rend="indent">and hair garlands where bees abound.</l>
<l>If we speak [honestly], dark sea-hued lord,</l>
<l rend="indent">you think she is water that you have in your cheek.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
